data.description: This quiet country home is situated on the backside of a sprawling 35 acre lot near sunny hills with stocked ponds and loads of wildlife. Partially fenced for livestock and plenty of room for a garden or two. All tile floors. New ac unit in 2022. New metal roof in 2020. New heated gunite pool with full enclosure completed January 2023. Pole barn with 30 amp rv hookup.15 minutes to Chipley 25 minutes to Panama City. Must see in person to truly appreciate!
